1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
From its humble beginnings in the early 20th
century, IIT (ISM) Dhanbad has forged an
extraordinary legacy, transforming vision into
impactful reality.

2
00:00:08,250 --> 00:00:16,250
Established in 1926, this esteemed institution has
stood tall for nearly a century, steadily evolving
through the millennium.

3
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:24,500
What began as the Indian School of Mines has
blossomed into a full-fledged Indian Institute of
Technology, operating with 18 vibrant branches
across Engineering, Applied Sciences, Management
Studies, and Humanities, cementing its place as a
prominent global institution.

4
00:00:24,750 --> 00:00:32,750
This transformation marks a new era, building upon
a centenary of outperforming achievements in both
academia and industry.

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Our campus is a hub of comprehensive learning,
offering a diverse array of undergraduate,
postgraduate, and PhD programs.

6
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:49,250
We foster a rich environment for research, leading
to groundbreaking contributions.

7
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:57,500
From pioneering the nation's first Geoarchaeology
course to a unique integrated BTech-MBA program
with IIM Mumbai, our academic offerings reflect a
commitment to forward-thinking education.

8
00:00:57,750 --> 00:01:05,750
Faculty members are not just educators but
innovators, with individuals like Prof Sekhar
Dutta becoming Fellows of the Institution of Civil
Engineers, UK, and Prof Anshumali shaping climate
change policy.

9
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Our researchers, like the team that conducted the
first-ever multiple-layered blasting using smart
design, are at the forefront of industrial
innovation.

10
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:22,250
IIT (ISM) Dhanbad shines on the global stage,
proudly securing the 20th position worldwide in
Engineering-Mineral and Mining in QS rankings, a
significant leap and a testament to our
specialized excellence.

11
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:30,500
Our reach extends beyond the campus gates through
vital community work, including skill development
programs for local youth and leadership training
for Panchayati Raj Functionaries.

12
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:38,750
We embrace inclusivity, as demonstrated by the
Uttar Pradesh government's support for Atul
Kumar's IIT education following Supreme Court
intervention, and our commitment to student well-
being through initiatives like a fully operational
campus creche.

13
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:47,000
Our alumni, such as Ms Gargi Mishra, recognized
among the top 100 inspiring women in mining
globally, continue to make us proud.

14
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:55,250
Even moments of campus joy, like the viral Diwali
rocket video, add to the vibrant tapestry of
student life.

15
00:01:55,500 --> 00:02:03,500
As we continue to drive India's critical mineral
mission and innovate in fields from Arctic MedTech
to Hydrogen Valley development, IIT (ISM) Dhanbad
remains dedicated to shaping future leaders and
contributing to a brighter tomorrow.

